00:15:09,333 --> 00:15:12,567
When i left my job,

319
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,834
a lot of people were furious with me.

320
00:15:14,867 --> 00:15:19,467
It was easier to be angry than|to admit they weren't happy.

321
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:22,134
