Could be psychogenic.

393
00:19:37,834 --> 00:19:39,467
She made big, sudden change in her life.

394
00:19:39,501 --> 00:19:40,634
Could be the result|of a mental imbalance.

395
00:19:40,701 --> 00:19:42,334
She wants to do what she wants to do.

396
00:19:42,401 --> 00:19:44,100
What's crazy about that?

397
00:19:44,134 --> 00:19:45,434
Why do you have to quit to do it?

