00:19:45,501 --> 00:19:46,900
If i want to do something, i do it.

399
00:19:46,967 --> 00:19:48,667
If you can figure out a|balance, there's no burnout.

400
00:19:48,701 --> 00:19:50,367
Thanks for the lesson, deepak.

401
00:19:50,401 --> 00:19:53,134
The itching started yesterday,|not eight months ago.

402
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,634
Meningitis, encephalitis...

