00:19:59,834 --> 00:20:01,334
Ms would explain, possibly the lungs.

406
00:20:01,401 --> 00:20:02,801
So would a brain tumor.

407
00:20:02,868 --> 00:20:03,834
Well, how 'bout we stop guessing

