00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:12,100
I don't remember demoting you.

424
00:21:12,167 --> 00:21:14,234
I brought you something.

425
00:21:14,267 --> 00:21:15,634
The latest issue of parent magazine.

426
00:21:15,701 --> 00:21:18,367
