503
00:24:27,234 --> 00:24:28,401
I can't see anything.

504
00:24:44,701 --> 00:24:46,601
You gonna tip housekeeping?

505
00:24:46,634 --> 00:24:49,067
Get it from cuddy.

506
00:24:49,134 --> 00:24:50,334
